02:16:20.34 --> 02:16:23.74
I can't remember, anyway, it doesn't matter.

2941
02:16:23.74 --> 02:16:26.18
Sims, nice guy, nice guy.

2942
02:16:26.18 --> 02:16:28.30
At any rate, I would turn,

2943
02:16:28.30 --> 02:16:30.30
I would orbit to the right,

2944
02:16:30.30 --> 02:16:33.74
and I knew that he was gonna roll in from 1-8.

2945
02:16:33.74 --> 02:16:38.22
I would roll in anywhere at the top of the quadrant

2946
02:16:39.70 --> 02:16:42.62
of the compass rows.

2947
02:16:42.62 --> 02:16:45.66
