02:19:08.14 --> 02:19:11.66
have a dozen paper towel tubes taped together,

3001
02:19:11.66 --> 02:19:15.98
he can hear you, even if you got your engines at idle,

3002
02:19:15.98 --> 02:19:18.06
I think, that's my private theory,

3003
02:19:18.06 --> 02:19:19.90
I don't know if that's true or not,

3004
02:19:19.90 --> 02:19:21.94
but anyway, that's when they would open up on you,

3005
02:19:21.94 --> 02:19:25.02
and yes, every night, no question, every night,

3006
02:19:25.02 --> 02:19:29.06
anytime you were there, they would blast away,

3007
02:19:30.34 --> 02:19:31.50
and...

