02:20:43.38 --> 02:20:47.02
you have a responsibility to, in your book,

3036
02:20:47.02 --> 02:20:51.86
you talk about things that are worth it

3037
02:20:51.86 --> 02:20:53.10
and things that are not worth it,

3038
02:20:53.10 --> 02:20:55.34
and I have to tell anybody who's willing to,

3039
02:20:55.34 --> 02:20:58.06
including my old skipper or somebody like that,

